# =============================================================================
# AI News Daily Digest — environment template
# =============================================================================
# 1. Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values:
#       cp .env.example .env
# 2. .env is git-ignored; NEVER commit it.
#
# ⚠️  SECURITY WARNING
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# If this `.env` file (or the values it contains) has ever been committed
# to a public repo, posted in chat, or otherwise shared, ROTATE these
# keys IMMEDIATELY:
#   * DeepSeek API key:   https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys
#   * Feishu webhook:     Feishu group → 群机器人 → 重置 / 删除后重新添加
# Also re-check git history (`git log -p -- .env`) for past leaks.
# --------------------------------------------------------------------

# === AI Provider (choose one in config.yaml: ai.provider) ===
# Supported: deepseek (default) | openai | ollama | rule

# DeepSeek API Key (required if ai.provider = deepseek)
# Get yours at: https://platform.deepseek.com/api_keys
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...

# OpenAI API Key (required if ai.provider = openai)
OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Ollama base URL (default: http://localhost:11434, used if ai.provider = ollama)
OLLAMA_BASE_URL=http://localhost:11434

# === Feishu Bot Webhook ===
# Webhook URL — required
FEISHU_WEBHOOK_URL=https://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/bot/v2/hook/xxxxxxxxxx

# Webhook signing secret — optional but recommended.
# When non-empty, every outgoing payload is signed with HMAC-SHA256
# (timestamp + secret) per Feishu's webhook spec. To enforce it, enable
# "签名校验" in the bot's 安全设置 page. The two values MUST match.
FEISHU_WEBHOOK_SECRET=